    mainHeader: `Charlie Hunnam verified reports of his potential comeback to Sons of Anarchy.`,
    subHeader: "",
    contentHeader: `Charlie Hunnam verified reports of his potential comeback to Sons of Anarchy.`,
    content: "<p class='first'>Charlie Hunnam, the actor who played the lead character in the hit TV show 'Sons of Anarchy,' has recently been the subject of rumors that he may return to the show. While many fans are excited about the possibility of Hunnam reprising his role as Jax Teller, there has been no official confirmation from the show's creators or Hunnam himself.</p><p>The rumors began when a fan site posted a story claiming that Hunnam had signed on to appear in a new 'Sons of Anarchy' spin-off series. However, this story has not been confirmed by any reputable sources, and Hunnam has not made any public statements indicating that he will be returning to the show.</p><p>It's important to note that actors often have busy schedules and may not be able to return to a show even if they want to. Additionally, show creators may decide to go in a different direction with the story, which could prevent the return of certain characters.</p><p>In Hunnam’s case, he has hinted his reappearance on the beloved fan franchise but has also stated that his return may not be in the form that most fans would expect. </p><p>My thought process was: <i>Hmmmm Ok! Interesting! Now I can’t wait! I was actually obsessed with this show and watched it thrice!!!. Anyways… moving on.</i></p><div><img src='/images/charlieHunnam-2.jpg' class='block m-auto  md:pt-5 object-cover' /><p class='text-center text-sm py-1 max-w-[600px] m-auto'>Image source:<a href='https://people.com/tv/charlie-hunnam-reflects-on-impact-of-sons-of-anarchy/'>FX/COURTESY EVERETT</a></p></div><p>While it's understandable that fans of 'Sons of Anarchy' would be excited about the possibility of Hunnam returning to the show, it's important to wait for official confirmation before getting too invested in the idea. In the meantime, fans can continue to enjoy the original series and speculate about what the future may hold for the world of SAMCRO.</p>",
    month: "MAR 2023 EDITION",
    img: "/images/charlieHunnam-1.jpg",
